{"tid":439194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對旺角大媽既睇法","createTime":"2017-10-17T14:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T15:25:40.000Z","uid":61864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40a6710ebe77331c40e6393ef47efa7e5bd00638","tid":439194,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"頭先睇到有個post，主要係講對旺角大媽既睇法同不滿，而且好多人都認為要趕佢地走、光復旺角等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我又講下自己既睇法&hellip;假設政府真係立法取消旺角行人專用區，我唔認為班大媽會咁易就放棄唱歌跳舞。所以佢地會去返自己住個區繼續唱，到時就唔只旺角嘈，全香港都係大媽既歌聲。既然係咁，不如有得佢哋係旺角唱到2046。<br />\n<br />\n可能我咁既諗法有啲負面，但真係冇咩 實際嘅方法解決呢個問題。"},{"pid":"a80954b4d24c3694bf82817a3844890df041fe15","tid":439194,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ab2e9fce2b5a589c7834918735a03906e5fa0a4","tid":439194,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘅</strong></span><br />\n地<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>哋</strong></span><br />\n個<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嗰</strong></span><br />\n係咁<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>係噉</strong></span><br />\n有得佢<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>由得佢</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png&h=97dc3c33&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\nok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7dad7bac4df588a52d018cd57571296b78530e","tid":439194,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb277ec9de1faf587e60c627861e626b3bb24794","tid":439194,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你屋企開party任人嚟玩，有個乞兒晚晚嚟你屋企乞食，你就諗，趕走佢佢都會去第二度乞㗎啦，不如唔趕走佢，等佢日日喺我屋企算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad