d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可以趕佢地去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n趕返大陸....雖然冇可能。<br />\n去到邊趕到邊，趕到佢地要去收費區跳<br />\n（eg party 房）</blockquote><br />\n用大媽既角度諗，佢地會比錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f404fabdac825363b96bbc9ebb5405df411c6ef0","tid":439194,"uid":136773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:15:19.000Z","msg":"大媽跳舞 人人喊打"},{"pid":"9f3c0bd093876fa9616e84eb9df3b8356a385655","tid":439194,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你屋企開party任人嚟玩，有個乞兒晚晚嚟你屋企乞食，你就諗，趕走佢佢都會去第二度乞㗎啦，不如唔趕走佢，等佢日日喺我屋企算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係依家情況唔是趕唔走班乞兒之餘 連自己屋企都俾人抄埋家咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果下次個乞兒去其他巴打屋企咁未又封多獲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係班乞兒有心要玩鳩你想你封屋既話 咁未碌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}